<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich III. von Aufseß, Bischof von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Nachsicht wegen der Steuerforderung des Adressaten an das Katharinenkloster zu Nürnberg, da dessen Armleute derzeit unter den Kriegshandlungen zu leiden haben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_327" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l12"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Ervveltem cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l13">Byſſchoff ʒu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l14"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürbraht ~ die <expan>pflege<ex>r</ex></expan> der <expan>geiſtlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l16">frawen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l15">des Cloſters </ab></add> hie cʒu ſant kathrein . vvie ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> ſtewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l17">auf ſie gelegt hab . des ſie cʒu der cʒeit 
<del rend="strikethrough">gar </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_327_line_1577277664748_1179">
<del rend="strikethrough">vaſt </del></ab></add> vndürfftig ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l18">nemlich daʒ Jn Jr Armlewte in dem kryge gar vaſt beſcheydig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l20">woꝛden ſein . 
<del rend="strikethrough">hyrüm </del> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſie darynne von </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">ewr </del></ab></add> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>
<del rend="strikethrough">n</del></expan> gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l23">
<del rend="strikethrough">gnediklich wöllet günſtiklich <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l21">cʒu Jn wenden </ab></add> vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l22">Jn darynn </ab></add> gne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r2l26">dig ſein 
<add><ab facs="#facs_327_r2l24">wöllet </ab></add> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_327" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, erweltem czu bysschoff zu Bamberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürbraht die
                                                  <expan>pflege<ex>r</ex></expan> der
                                                  <expan>geistlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frawen
                                                  <add>des closters</add> hie czu sant Kathrein, wie
                                                ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> stewr auf sie
                                                gelegt hab, des sie czu der czeit undürfftig sein
                                                nemlich, daz in ir armlewte in dem kryge gar vast
                                                bescheydig worden sein.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <add>czu in
                                                  wenden</add> und <add>in darynn</add> gnedig sein
                                                  <add>wöllet</add> durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
